  "content": "<p>Just because it&#8217;s summertime doesn&#8217;t mean that there aren&#8217;t some amazing squash events. And of the best and most fun is at the <a href=\"http://jerichotennisclub.com/Activities/Squash\">Jericho Club</a> in Vancouver every year, for the Sun and Surf Tournament in August. ESC member Brad Salter went this year representing the ESC, along with the recently departed John Clarkin who moved to Calgary this year.</p>\n<p>With incredible food and only an $80 entry fee, this is one of the best value tournaments around. Courts are only 20 steps from the beach. It&#8217;s also in an incredibly beautiful and walkable area of Vancouver. If you&#8217;re out there next year, this tournament is highly recommended.</p>\n<p>Congrats to Brad for winning the B consolation final!</p>\n<div id='gallery-1' class='gallery galleryid-4816 gallery-columns-2 gallery-size-medium'><figure class='gallery-item'>\n\t\t\t<div class='gallery-icon landscape'>\n\t\t\t\t<a href='https://edmontonsquashclub.ca/summer-tournament-adventure-sun-and-surf-2018-at-the-jericho-club/img_3939/#main'><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"300\" height=\"150\" src=\"https://edmontonsquashclub.ca/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/IMG_3939-300x150.jpg\" class=\"attachment-medium size-medium\" alt=\"\" aria-describedby=\"gallery-1-4835\" srcset=\"https://edmontonsquashclub.ca/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/IMG_3939-300x150.jpg 300w, https://edmontonsquashclub.ca/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/IMG_3939-20x10.jpg 20w, https://edmontonsquashclub.ca/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/IMG_3939.jpg 612w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" /></a>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t<figcaption class='wp-caption-text gallery-caption' id='gallery-1-4835'>\n\t\t\t\tThe Jericho Club\n\t\t\t\t</figcaption></figure><figure class='gallery-item'>\n\t\t\t<div class='gallery-icon portrait'>\n\t\t\t\t<a href='https://edmontonsquashclub.ca/summer-tournament-adventure-sun-and-surf-2018-at-the-jericho-club/img_3944/#main'><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"150\" height=\"300\" src=\"https://edmontonsquashclub.ca/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/IMG_3944-150x300.jpg\" class=\"attachment-medium size-medium\" alt=\"\" aria-describedby=\"gallery-1-4836\" srcset=\"https://edmontonsquashclub.ca/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/IMG_3944-150x300.jpg 150w, https://edmontonsquashclub.ca/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/IMG_3944-10x20.jpg 10w, https://edmontonsquashclub.ca/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/IMG_3944.jpg 320w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px\" /></a>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t<figcaption class='wp-caption-text gallery-caption' id='gallery-1-4836'>\n\t\t\t\tJohn Clarkin at the Sun and Surf 2018 Tournament\n\t\t\t\t</figcaption></figure><figure class='gallery-item'>\n\t\t\t<div class='gallery-icon portrait'>\n\t\t\t\t<a href='https://edmontonsquashclub.ca/summer-tournament-adventure-sun-and-surf-2018-at-the-jericho-club/img_3945/#main'><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"225\" height=\"300\" src=\"https://edmontonsquashclub.ca/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/IMG_3945-225x300.jpg\" class=\"attachment-medium size-medium\" alt=\"\" aria-describedby=\"gallery-1-4837\" srcset=\"https://edmontonsquashclub.ca/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/IMG_3945-225x300.jpg 225w, https://edmontonsquashclub.ca/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/IMG_3945-15x20.jpg 15w, https://edmontonsquashclub.ca/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/IMG_3945.jpg 612w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 225px) 100vw, 225px\" /></a>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t<figcaption class='wp-caption-text gallery-caption' id='gallery-1-4837'>\n\t\t\t\tBrad Salter at the Sun and Surf 2018 Tournament\n\t\t\t\t</figcaption></figure><figure class='gallery-item'>\n\t\t\t<div class='gallery-icon portrait'>\n\t\t\t\t<a href='https://edmontonsquashclub.ca/summer-tournament-adventure-sun-and-surf-2018-at-the-jericho-club/img_3946/#main'><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"225\" height=\"300\" src=\"https://edmontonsquashclub.ca/wp-content/uploads/2